" async=\"\"></script><script src=\"/_next/static/chunks/0a2ii1vvh49-w.js\" async=\"\"></script><script src=\"/_next/static/chunks/turbopack-17o0es9ykmxg8.js\" async=\"\"></script><script src=\"/_next/static/chunks/0hj~9o58ixdn5.js\" async=\"\"></script><script src=\"/_next/static/chunks/0ogutoh6z79ck.js\" async=\"\"></script><script src=\"/_next/static/chunks/06_r48v~ia_p1.js\" async=\"\"></script><script src=\"/_next/static/chunks/0y4tqwm5g3udo.js\" async=\"\"></script><link rel=\"preload\" href=\"/ticpin-logo-black.png\" as=\"image\"/><meta name=\"next-size-adjust\" content=\"\"/><title>Ticpin | Explore Dining, Events, &amp; Play Venues</title><meta name=\"description\" content=\"Your ultimate gateway to world-class sports, entertainment, and dining. Book events, find sports venues, and discover the best dining experiences on Ticpin.\"/><meta name=\"author\" content=\"Ticpin Team\"/><meta name=\"keywords\" content=\"Ticpin,Dining,Events,Sports,Booking,Entertainment\"/><meta property=\"og:title\" content=\"Ticpin | Explore Dining, Events, &amp; Play Venues\"/><meta property=\"og:description\" content=\"Your ultimate gateway to world-class sports, entertainment, and dining.\"/><meta property=\"og:url\" content=\"https://ticpin.com\"/><meta property=\"og:site_name\" content=\"Ticpin\"/><meta property=\"og:type\" content=\"website\"/><meta name=\"twitter:card\" content=\"summary\"/><meta name=\"twitter:title\" content=\"Ticpin | Explore Dining, Events, &amp; Play Venues\"/><meta name=\"twitter:description\" content=\"Your ultimate gateway to world-class sports, entertainment, and dining.\"/><link rel=\"shortcut icon\" href=\"/favicon.ico\"/><link rel=\"icon\" href=\"/favicon.ico\" sizes=\"any\"/><link rel=\"icon\" href=\"/favicon.jpg\" type=\"image/jpeg\"/><link rel=\"apple-touch-icon\" href=\"/favicon.jpg\"/><script src=\"/_next/static/chunks/03~yq9q893hmn.js\" noModule=\"\"></script></head><body class=\"anek_latin_235243e6-module__hdzBgW__variable inter_5f5ee935-module__rY2UjW__variable anek_tamil_c8d41f5c-module__KNtQ0G__variable anektamilcondensed_9c773438-module__lW4LeG__variable font-sans antialiased text-black overflow-x-hidden w-full\"><div hidden=\"\"><!--$--><!--/$--></div><!--$--><!--/$--><!--$--><div class=\"min-h-screen bg-white font-[family-name:var(--font-anek-latin)]\"><header class=\"w-full h-20 flex items-center justify-center border-b border-[#D9D9D9]\"><div class=\"relative h-8 md:h-9 w-[159px]\"><img alt=\"TICPIN\" loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" data-nimg=\"fill\" class=\"object-contain\" style=\"position:absolute;height:100%;width:100%;left:0;top:0;right:0;bottom:0;color:transparent\" sizes=\"100vw\" srcSet=\"/_next/image?url=%2Fticpin-logo-black.png&amp;w=640&amp;q=75 640w, /_next/image?url=%2Fticpin-logo-black.png&amp;w=750&amp;q=75 750w, /_next/image?url=%2Fticpin-logo-black.png&amp;w=828&amp;q=75 828w, /_next/image?url=%2Fticpin-logo-black.png&amp;w=1080&amp;q=75 1080w, /_next/image?url=%2Fticpin-logo-black.png&amp;w=1200&amp;q=75 1200w, /_next/image?url=%2Fticpin-logo-black.png&amp;w=1920&amp;q=75 1920w, /_next/image?url=%2Fticpin-logo-black.png&amp;w=2048&amp;q=75 2048w, /_next/image?url=%2Fticpin-logo-black.png&amp;w=3840&amp;q=75 3840w\" src=\"/_next/image?url=%2Fticpin-logo-black.png&amp;w=3840&amp;q=75\"/></div></header><main class=\"max-w-[1100px] mx-auto px-6 py-16 mt-[-10px]\"><h1 class=\"text-[34px] font-semibold text-black text-center mb-10 break-words\" style=\"font-family:Anek Latin\">Privacy policy</h1><div class=\"max-w-none text-[#686868] font-medium text-[18px] leading-relaxed space-y-10\" style=\"font-family:Anek Latin\"><div><p class=\"italic mb-6\">Last Updated: FEB 22, 2026</p><h2 class=\"text-black text-[22px] font-bold mb-4\">Your Privacy Matters</h2><p>Velora Technologies Private Limited, the owner and operator of the Ticpin platform, respects your privacy and is committed to protecting your personal data. By accessing or using the Platform, you consent to the practices described in this Privacy Policy.</p></div><div class=\"space-y-6\"><div class=\"space-y-2\"><h2 class=\"text-black text-[22px] font-bold\">Scope of This Privacy Policy</h2><div class=\"space-y-4\"><p>This Privacy Policy applies to all users of the Platform, including customers, organizers, merchants, vendors, and visitors. This Policy should be read together with the Ticpin Terms &amp; Conditions.</p></div></div><div class=\"space-y-2\"><h2 class=\"text-black text-[22px] font-bold\">Information We Collect</h2><div class=\"space-y-4\"><div class=\"space-y-2\"><h3 class=\"text-black font-bold\">Personal Information</h3><p>We may collect the following personal information:</p><ul class=\"list-disc pl-6 space-y-1\"><li>Name</li><li>Mobile number</li><li>Email address</li><li>Date of birth (where required)</li><li>Account login details</li><li>Preferences and profile information</li></ul></div><div class=\"space-y-2\"><h3 class=\"text-black font-bold\">Payment Information</h3><p>All payments are processed through authorized third-party payment gateways. Ticpin does not store your complete debit card, credit card, or UPI details.</p></div><div class=\"space-y-2\"><h3 class=\"text-black font-bold\">Usage &amp; Technical Data</h3><p>We may collect:</p><ul class=\"list-disc pl-6 space-y-1\"><li>Device and browser information</li><li>IP address and log data</li><li>Location data (approximate or precise, subject to permission)</li><li>App usage behavior, searches, clicks, and booking history</li></ul></div><div class=\"space-y-2\"><h3 class=\"text-black font-bold\">User-Generated Content</h3><p>We may collect:</p><ul class=\"list-disc pl-6 space-y-1\"><li>Reviews, ratings, comments</li><li>Photos, videos, and messages shared on the Platform</li><li>Communications with customer support</li></ul></div><div class=\"space-y-2\"><h3 class=\"text-black font-bold\">Information from Third Parties</h3><p>We may receive information from event organizers, merchants, payment providers, analytics partners, or marketing partners.</p></div></div></div><div class=\"space-y-2\"><h2 class=\"text-black text-[22px] font-bold\">How We Use Your Information</h2><div class=\"space-y-4\"><p>We use collected information to:</p><ul class=\"list-disc pl-6 space-y-1\"><li>Create and manage user accounts</li><li>Enable ticket bookings and reservations</li><li>Process payments and confirmations</li><li>Provide customer support</li><li>Send transactional, service, and promotional communications</li><li>Personalize content and recommendations</li><li>Improve platform features and performance</li><li>Detect and prevent fraud, misuse, and security incidents</li><li>Comply with legal and regulatory obligations</li></ul></div></div><div class=\"space-y-2\"><h2 class=\"text-black text-[22px] font-bold\">Legal Basis for Processing</h2><div class=\"space-y-4\"><p>We process personal data based on:</p><ul class=\"list-disc pl-6 space-y-1\"><li>Your consent</li><li>Performance of a contract</li><li>Compliance with legal obligations</li><li>Legitimate business interests</li></ul></div></div><div class=\"space-y-2\"><h2 class=\"text-black text-[22px] font-bold\">Cookies and Tracking Technologies</h2><div class=\"space-y-4\"><p>We use cookies, SDKs, and similar technologies to enhance user experience, analyze usage, and improve Services. You may control cookies through your device or browser settings, but disabling them may affect Platform functionality.</p></div></div><div class=\"space-y-2\"><h2 class=\"text-black text-[22px] font-bold\">Sharing of Information</h2><div class=\"space-y-4\"><div class=\"space-y-2\"><h3 class=\"text-black font-bold\">Organizers &amp; Merchants</h3><p>To fulfill bookings, manage entries, and provide event-related services.</p></div><div class=\"space-y-2\"><h3 class=\"text-black font-bold\">Service Providers</h3><p>Including cloud hosting, analytics, communication, and customer support providers.</p></div><div class=\"space-y-2\"><h3 class=\"text-black font-bold\">Payment Partners</h3><p>For secure processing of transactions.</p></div><div class=\"space-y-2\"><h3 class=\"text-black font-bold\">Legal Authorities</h3><p>When required by law, court order, or governmental request.</p></div><div class=\"space-y-2\"><h3 class=\"text-black font-bold\">Business Transfers</h3><p>In the event of a merger, acquisition, or sale of assets.</p></div><p class=\"pt-2\">We do not sell your personal data to third parties.</p></div></div><div class=\"space-y-2\"><h2 class=\"text-black text-[22px] font-bold\">Data Retention</h2><div class=\"space-y-4\"><p>We retain personal data only as long as necessary to provide Services, comply with legal obligations, resolve disputes, and enforce agreements.</p></div></div><div class=\"space-y-2\"><h2 class=\"text-black text-[22px] font-bold\">Data Security</h2><div class=\"space-y-4\"><p>We implement reasonable administrative, technical, and physical safeguards to protect your data. However, no method of transmission or storage is completely secure, and we cannot guarantee absolute security.</p></div></div><div class=\"space-y-2\"><h2 class=\"text-black text-[22px] font-bold\">Your Rights and Choices</h2><div class=\"space-y-4\"><p>Subject to applicable law, you may:</p><ul class=\"list-disc pl-6 space-y-1\"><li>Access or update your personal information</li><li>Withdraw consent for marketing communications</li><li>Request account deletion</li><li>Request correction or deletion of data</li></ul><p>Requests can be made through the Platform or via official support channels.</p></div></div><div class=\"space-y-2\"><h2 class=\"text-black text-[22px] font-bold\">Children&#x27;s Privacy</h2><div class=\"space-y-4\"><p>The Platform is not intended for independent use by individuals under 18 years of age. Minors may use the Platform only under parental or legal guardian supervision.</p></div></div><div class=\"space-y-2\"><h2 class=\"text-black text-[22px] font-bold\">Changes to This Privacy Policy</h2><div class=\"space-y-4\"><p>We may update this Privacy Policy from time to time. Continued use of the Platform after changes constitutes acceptance of the revised Policy.</p></div></div></div><div class=\"pt-10 border-t border-zinc-200\"><h2 class=\"text-black text-[22px] font-bold mb-4\">Grievance Redressal &amp; Contact</h2><p>For questions, concerns, or grievances related to this Privacy Policy or your data, please contact us through the support channels available on the Platform.</p><p class=\"mt-6 font-bold text-black\">By using Ticpin, you acknowledge that you have read, understood, and agreed to this Privacy Policy.</p></div></div></main></div><!--$--><!--/$--><!--/$--><div class=\"fixed top-4 right-4 z-50 space-y-2\"></div><script src=\"/_next/static/chunks/149tn1xfdacy4.js\" id=\"_R_\" async=\"\"></script><script>(self.__next_f=self.__next_f||[]).push([0])</script><script>self.__next_f.push([1,\"1:I[487236,[\\\"/_next/static/chunks/0hj~9o58ixdn5.js\\\",\\\"/_next/static/chunks/0ogutoh6z79ck.js\\\",\\\"/_next/static/chunks/06_r48v~ia_p1.js\\\"],\\\"LoadingBoundaryProvider\\\"]\\n2:\\\"$Sreact.fragment\\\"\\n3:I[888840,[\\\"/_next/static/chunks/0hj~9o58ixdn5.js\\\",\\\"/_next/static/chunks/0ogutoh6z79ck.js\\\",\\\"/_next/static/chunks/06_r48v~ia_p1.js\\\"],\\\"ToastProvider\\\"]\\n4:I[801801,[\\\"/_next/static/chunks/0hj~9o58ixdn5.js\\\",\\\"/_next/static/chunks/0ogutoh6z79ck.js\\\",\\\"/_next/static/chunks/06_r48v~ia_p1.js\\\"],\\\"default\\\"]\\n5:I[246417,[\\\"/_next/static/chunks/0hj~9o58ixdn5.js\\\",\\\"/_next/static/chunks/0ogutoh6z79ck.js\\\",\\\"/_next/static/chunks/06_r48v~ia_p1.js\\\"],\\\"default\\\"]\\n6:\\\"$Sreact.suspense\\\"\\n7:I[710088,[\\\"/_next/static/chunks/0hj~9o58ixdn5.js\\\",\\\"/_next/static/chunks/0ogutoh6z79ck.js\\\",\\\"/_next/static/chunks/06_r48v~ia_p1.js\\\"],\\\"default\\\"]\\n8:I[487236,[\\\"/_next/static/chunks/0hj~9o58ixdn5.js\\\",\\\"/_next/static/chunks/0ogutoh6z79ck.js\\\",\\\"/_next/static/chunks/06_r48v~ia_p1.js\\\"]